Vital Point 5
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b Black to Play.\b0
\par If you are afraid of your stones getting captured, you can't save black.
\par
\par The solution is not a common move. It's unusual.
\par
\par The first move is the key!
\par }
