Diagram 1 (Correct)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Did you found black's throw-in move at B1?
\par
\par If you came to think of this move, the problem is as good as solved.
\par
\par White can only capture with 2.
\par
\par Now when black plays dansu at 3, white is trapped and does not have the liberties necessary to connect.
\par
\par Black lives beautifully.
\par }
