Diagram 2 (A Bent Three)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It seems like a common move for black to capture white at 1. In fact, it is commonly helpless.
\par
\par When white plays 2, black can only die.
\par }
