Diagram 3 (No Way to Live)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's dansu at 1 can't save the black group either.
\par White simply connects at 2. Even a beginner can play white 2 correctly.
\par
\par Even if black captures the three white stones, living is impossible.
\par }
